data.description:
Introducing your new cozy corner retreat at 446 W Bloxham St! Get ready to fall in love with this sunny 2-story, 2-bed, 2 1/2-bath townhouse in east Lantana. Just a hop, skip, and a jump away from the beach, Old Key Lime House, cool shops and diners.Inside, you'll find a neat kitchen and a cool bar that connects to the living area. And guess what? Updated stainless steel appliances and a fresh washer & dryer are all yours to enjoy!Oh, and did we mention it's a corner unit? That means extra windows flooding the place with tons of natural light. Downstairs, there's a handy 1/2 bath and laundry room, plus sleek luxury vinyl flooring on the second floor. Upstairs? Two big bedrooms, each with their own bathroom. Oh, and don't worry about storms - this place is all set with accordion shutters.
And guess what else? The HOA community has its own pool and a fun playground for kids. And hey, the HOA fees won't break the bank!
Pet friendly, Come check out your new digs - you're gonna love it here!
